---
import ClientReportLayout from '../../../layouts/ClientReportLayout.astro';
---

<ClientReportLayout title="Website Audit & Scorecard" clientName="1st Home Maintenance">
<nav class="top-nav">
  <div class="container">
    <a href="/clients/zolley/" class="nav-brand">Brothers Automate</a>
    <a href="/clients/zolley/">&larr; Back to Overview</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-badge">Website Audit & Scorecard</div>
    <h1>Your Site is Fast. But Nobody Can Find It.</h1>
    <p>Outstanding technical performance, but critical gaps in content, local visibility, and social presence are keeping you off the map.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="score-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="score-ring-container">
      <svg width="200" height="200" viewBox="0 0 200 200">
        <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="85" fill="none" stroke="#f1f5f9" stroke-width="12"/>
        <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="85" fill="none" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="12" stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-dasharray="534" stroke-dashoffset="331"/>
      </svg>
      <div class="score-ring-text">
        <div class="number score-amber">38</div>
        <div class="label">out of 100</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="score-grade">Your site has a strong technical foundation, but major gaps in content, local search, and social media bring your overall marketing readiness score down significantly.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="categories-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="categories-grid">
      <div class="category-card">
        <div class="cat-score score-green">9</div>
        <div class="cat-max">/ 10</div>
        <div class="cat-name">Performance</div>
        <div class="cat-bar"><div class="cat-bar-fill bar-green" style="width: 90%"></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="category-card">
        <div class="cat-score score-green">7</div>
        <div class="cat-max">/ 10</div>
        <div class="cat-name">Technical Health</div>
        <div class="cat-bar"><div class="cat-bar-fill bar-green" style="width: 70%"></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="category-card">
        <div class="cat-score score-red">2</div>
        <div class="cat-max">/ 10</div>
        <div class="cat-name">Content Freshness</div>
        <div class="cat-bar"><div class="cat-bar-fill bar-red" style="width: 20%"></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="category-card">
        <div class="cat-score score-red">1</div>
        <div class="cat-max">/ 10</div>
        <div class="cat-name">Local Visibility</div>
        <div class="cat-bar"><div class="cat-bar-fill bar-red" style="width: 10%"></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="category-card">
        <div class="cat-score score-red">0</div>
        <div class="cat-max">/ 10</div>
        <div class="cat-name">Social Presence</div>
        <div class="cat-bar"><div class="cat-bar-fill bar-red" style="width: 2%"></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="findings-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">Detailed Findings</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">What We Found</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">Click any finding to expand the details.</p>

    <div class="finding-card open">
      <div class="finding-header" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
        <span class="finding-dot red"></span>
        <span class="finding-title">No Google Business Profile -- You're invisible on Maps</span>
        <span class="finding-category">Local</span>
        <svg class="finding-chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="finding-body">
        <p>A Google Business Profile is the single most impactful thing a local service business can do for online visibility. Without one, you don't appear in the map pack that shows up at the top of search results for "handyman boca raton" and similar queries. Your competitors Mr. Handyman (286 reviews), Tom & Son (71 reviews), and Best Boca (67 reviews) all dominate this space.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="finding-card">
      <div class="finding-header" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
        <span class="finding-dot red"></span>
        <span class="finding-title">Zero reviews on any platform</span>
        <span class="finding-category">Reputation</span>
        <svg class="finding-chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="finding-body">
        <p>We checked Google, Yelp, BBB, Angi, and Glassdoor. You have zero reviews on every platform. For local service businesses, reviews are the #1 factor potential customers use to decide who to call. Even 10 reviews would dramatically increase trust and conversion rates.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="finding-card">
      <div class="finding-header" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
        <span class="finding-dot red"></span>
        <span class="finding-title">No social media presence at all</span>
        <span class="finding-category">Social</span>
        <svg class="finding-chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="finding-body">
        <p>No Facebook page, no Instagram account, no Yelp listing, no BBB listing. Your competitors are active on multiple platforms. A Facebook Business Page alone would give you another place to collect reviews, share project photos, and appear in searches.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="finding-card">
      <div class="finding-header" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
        <span class="finding-dot red"></span>
        <span class="finding-title">Only 6 pages on the entire website</span>
        <span class="finding-category">Content</span>
        <svg class="finding-chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="finding-body">
        <p>Your site has: home, about, contact, drywall-repair, handyman-services, and home-repairs. That's it. Each page is a chance to rank for a different set of keywords. You're leaving thousands of potential search visitors on the table by not having dedicated pages for plumbing, electrical, bathroom remodeling, kitchen repair, ceiling fan installation, and more.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="finding-card">
      <div class="finding-header" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
        <span class="finding-dot red"></span>
        <span class="finding-title">Using Gmail instead of professional domain email</span>
        <span class="finding-category">Brand</span>
        <svg class="finding-chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="finding-body">
        <p>Your contact email is 1sthomemaint@gmail.com. A professional email like info@handymanbocaratonfl.com signals credibility and helps with deliverability. This is a quick win that takes 30 minutes to set up.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="finding-card">
      <div class="finding-header" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
        <span class="finding-dot amber"></span>
        <span class="finding-title">Missing meta descriptions on About and Contact pages</span>
        <span class="finding-category">Technical</span>
        <svg class="finding-chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="finding-body">
        <p>Your About and Contact pages don't have meta descriptions. Google will auto-generate these, but they won't be optimized for clicks. Writing custom meta descriptions takes 5 minutes per page and can increase click-through rates 20-30%.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="finding-card">
      <div class="finding-header" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
        <span class="finding-dot amber"></span>
        <span class="finding-title">Duplicate H1 tag on Contact page</span>
        <span class="finding-category">Technical</span>
        <svg class="finding-chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="finding-body">
        <p>Your Contact page has a duplicate H1 heading tag. Each page should have exactly one H1 that clearly describes the page content. This is a simple fix in WordPress.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="finding-card">
      <div class="finding-header" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
        <span class="finding-dot green"></span>
        <span class="finding-title">Excellent site speed and performance (97/100)</span>
        <span class="finding-category">Performance</span>
        <svg class="finding-chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="finding-body">
        <p>Your site scores 97/100 on performance on both desktop and mobile. This is outstanding and better than most competitor websites. WP Rocket is doing its job well. You also score 97/100 on accessibility and 100/100 on SEO technical setup via Yoast.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="finding-card">
      <div class="finding-header" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
        <span class="finding-dot green"></span>
        <span class="finding-title">Good tech stack: WordPress + Yoast SEO + WP Rocket</span>
        <span class="finding-category">Technical</span>
        <svg class="finding-chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="finding-body">
        <p>WordPress with Yoast SEO is an excellent foundation for growing your online presence. The SEO plugin makes it easy to optimize meta titles, descriptions, and schema markup. WP Rocket handles caching and performance. Google Analytics is installed for tracking. The tech foundation is solid -- it just needs more content to work with.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="actions-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">Priority Actions</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Top 8 Fixes, Ranked by Impact</h2>
    <ul class="action-list">
      <li class="action-item">
        <span class="action-priority high">1</span>
        <div class="action-text">
          <h4>Claim and optimize a Google Business Profile</h4>
          <p>This is the single highest-impact action. It unlocks Google Maps visibility, review collection, and local pack rankings.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="action-item">
        <span class="action-priority high">2</span>
        <div class="action-text">
          <h4>Start collecting Google reviews immediately</h4>
          <p>Text or email every past customer asking for a review. Even 10-15 reviews will put you on the map.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="action-item">
        <span class="action-priority high">3</span>
        <div class="action-text">
          <h4>Build 5+ service-specific landing pages</h4>
          <p>Plumbing repairs, electrical work, bathroom remodeling, kitchen repairs, ceiling fan installation. Each page targets new keywords.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="action-item">
        <span class="action-priority high">4</span>
        <div class="action-text">
          <h4>Create a Facebook Business Page</h4>
          <p>Free to set up, gives you another review platform, enables local advertising, and helps with social signals for SEO.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="action-item">
        <span class="action-priority med">5</span>
        <div class="action-text">
          <h4>Fix missing meta descriptions and duplicate H1</h4>
          <p>Quick technical fixes in Yoast SEO. 15 minutes of work that improves click-through rates.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="action-item">
        <span class="action-priority med">6</span>
        <div class="action-text">
          <h4>Set up professional domain email</h4>
          <p>Replace 1sthomemaint@gmail.com with info@handymanbocaratonfl.com for credibility.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="action-item">
        <span class="action-priority med">7</span>
        <div class="action-text">
          <h4>Add testimonials and project photos to the website</h4>
          <p>Social proof directly on your site builds trust before visitors even call.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="action-item">
        <span class="action-priority low">8</span>
        <div class="action-text">
          <h4>Create location pages for surrounding cities</h4>
          <p>Delray Beach, Boynton Beach, Deerfield Beach, Pompano Beach. Each one captures local search traffic.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Want Help Fixing These Issues?</h2>
    <p>We can walk you through the highest-impact changes and build a plan to get your score above 80.</p>
    <a href="https://cal.com/james-pinder-simpleflo/free-quiz-audit-automation-brothers" class="btn-cta">
      Book a Free Strategy Call
      <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="footer">
  <div class="container">Prepared by Brothers Automate &middot; April 2026</div>
</footer>
</ClientReportLayout>

<style is:global>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif; background: #fdfcfa; color: #1a365d; line-height: 1.6; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
    .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }

    .top-nav { padding: 1rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e6e1; background: #ffffff; }
    .top-nav .container { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
    .top-nav a { color: #64748b; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; }
    .top-nav a:hover { color: #1a365d; }
    .nav-brand { font-weight: 700; color: #1a365d !important; }

    /* Hero */
    .hero {
      padding: 100px 0 60px;
      text-align: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #78350f 0%, #f59e0b 50%, #92400e 100%);
      color: white;
    }
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
      border-radius: 9999px; padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4.5vw, 3rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 1rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }

    /* Overall Score */
    .score-section {
      padding: 60px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .score-ring-container {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .score-ring-container svg { transform: rotate(-90deg); }
    .score-ring-text {
      position: absolute;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .score-ring-text .number {
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .score-ring-text .label {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #64748b;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .score-grade {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #64748b;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* Category Scores */
    .categories-section {
      padding: 0 0 60px;
    }
    .categories-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .category-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e8e6e1;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .category-card .cat-score {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }
    .category-card .cat-max {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #94a3b8;
    }
    .category-card .cat-name {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-top: 0.75rem;
      color: #1a365d;
    }
    .category-card .cat-bar {
      height: 4px;
      background: #f1f5f9;
      border-radius: 2px;
      margin-top: 0.75rem;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .category-card .cat-bar-fill {
      height: 100%;
      border-radius: 2px;
      transition: width 1s ease;
    }
    .score-red { color: #dc2626; }
    .score-amber { color: #f59e0b; }
    .score-green { color: #16a34a; }
    .bar-red { background: #dc2626; }
    .bar-amber { background: #f59e0b; }
    .bar-green { background: #16a34a; }

    /* Findings */
    .findings-section {
      padding: 60px 0;
      background: #f8f7f4;
    }
    .section-label {
      font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #ed8936; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .section-title { font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .section-subtitle { color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 2rem; }

    .finding-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e8e6e1;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .finding-header {
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      user-select: none;
    }
    .finding-header:hover { background: #f8f7f4; }
    .finding-dot {
      width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .finding-dot.red { background: #dc2626; }
    .finding-dot.amber { background: #f59e0b; }
    .finding-dot.green { background: #16a34a; }
    .finding-title { font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; flex: 1; }
    .finding-category {
      font-size: 0.75rem; color: #94a3b8; font-weight: 500;
      background: #f8f7f4; padding: 0.2em 0.6em; border-radius: 9999px;
    }
    .finding-chevron {
      transition: transform 200ms ease;
      color: #94a3b8;
    }
    .finding-card.open .finding-chevron { transform: rotate(180deg); }
    .finding-body {
      display: none;
      padding: 0 1.25rem 1.25rem 2.75rem;
      color: #64748b;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .finding-card.open .finding-body { display: block; }

    /* Action Items */
    .actions-section { padding: 60px 0; }
    .action-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
    .action-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 1rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f0eeea;
    }
    .action-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .action-priority {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%;
      font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; color: white;
    }
    .action-priority.high { background: #dc2626; }
    .action-priority.med { background: #f59e0b; }
    .action-priority.low { background: #3182ce; }
    .action-text h4 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
    .action-text p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: #64748b; }

    /* CTA */
    .cta-section { background: #1a365d; padding: 60px 0; text-align: center; color: white; }
    .cta-section h2 { font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .cta-section p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
    .btn-cta {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
      background: #ed8936; color: white; padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none; transition: all 200ms ease;
    }
    .btn-cta:hover { background: #dd6b20; transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .footer { padding: 2rem 0; text-align: center; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #94a3b8; border-top: 1px solid #e8e6e1; }

    @media (max-width: 767px) {
      .categories-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    }
</style>

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
    var elements = document.querySelectorAll('.fade-up');
    if ('IntersectionObserver' in window) {
      var observer = new IntersectionObserver(function (entries) {
        entries.forEach(function (entry) {
          if (entry.isIntersecting) {
            entry.target.classList.add('visible');
            observer.unobserve(entry.target);
          }
        });
      }, { threshold: 0.15 });
      elements.forEach(function (el) { observer.observe(el); });
    } else {
      elements.forEach(function (el) { el.classList.add('visible'); });
    }
  });
</script>
